tasks.name: Lower Elwha Vaccination Event Flyer for 4/25
tasks.text_content:
Lower Elwha Health is holding a vaccine event planned for April 25th, 2023. They are asking for something similar to the other COVID flyers we have done for them. The client is requesting the flyer to include Native American representation and highlights the details of the event. The event 

Here are the details: 
Who: Lower Elwha Community
What: COVID vaccines for  ages 6 months and up, COVID boosters and flu vaccine 
Where: 2851 Lower Elwha Rd. Rm. 13
When: 5-8, during the Natural Resources Community dinner

Additionally, they have been offering a vaccine promotion ($200 for adult boosters, and $100 gift card for youth boosters), and they would like to add mention of this promotion on the flyer that its still available for LEKT community members. Applications can be found online: https://www.elwha.org/covid/covid-vaccine-support-programs/

As mentioned, the event will be taking place during a Natural Resources Community Dinner but the flyer doesn't have to look like the dinner flyer. They requested it look different.
